{"tid":1565274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"南區腐蝕液體案唔好殺錯良民","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:04:43.000Z","uid":68654,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c64b6eaba0cd3c80bc79b206c196e3e39cfded","tid":1565274,"uid":68654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:41:17.000Z","msg":"【利澤1837緊急澄清】<br />\n<br />\n第一次真心求share，因為1837住戶對小弟真係好好，每次行過都笑住叫我地加油&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n剛才，利澤1837對母子搵左我地，佢地表示，琴晚9點尾度婆婆已經訓左，而兒子亦都係度打機同睇戲，完全無參與任何有關投擲腐蝕性。如果大家認為有需要，佢地甚至唔介意邀請大家入屋搵證據，如果警方要收集佢地指紋，都會樂意配合。<br />\n<br />\n我明白，大家會覺得「叫得我地入去，一早毀滅哂證據」，但90幾歲既婆婆已經係泛民超過20年既義工，甚至會無視住邊度，吹雞一家大細孫仔孫女黎做義工，係真正既深黃銀髮族。<br />\n<br />\n我同大家一樣，極度希望搵到真兇，最好琴晚已經上樓拉人。但同時，現時未確定到究竟係15至18樓邊一戶掟出黎之前，胡亂行動好容易殺錯良民。<br />\n<br />\n另外，剛才婆婆搵我地時，有不少媒體都係度，相信大家好快會見到新聞錄像去講番件事。而婆婆既外傭當時幫婆婆卒完腳後，聽到巨響都入廚房睇，佢聲稱見到有玻璃樽係樓下單位飛出黎，但唔確定樓層。<br />\n<br />\n我地現時知道警方已經採取以下行動，並希望重案組盡快把握證據，捉拿真兇：<br />\n<br />\n1. 上樓問過疑似單位，包括1837；<br />\n2. 係掟落黎既物品收集指紋；<br />\n3. 睇過利澤樓升降機既閉路電視；<br />\n4. 睇過房署安裝既天眼閉路電視<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2280372081998458/posts/2420580187977646?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2280372081998458%2Fposts%2F2420580187977646%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=93bd1986\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2280372081998458/posts/2420580187977646?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"dc554b29bcb74537c383f728f6513a420452ce2a","tid":1565274,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3c3d692070d50084d4c3e5c7b681e5378aed534a","tid":1565274,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"409e922a1288bd5f87e78dcf90c8d3d336fd8c33","tid":1565274,"uid":68654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"依單野要追究到底<br />\n但唔好殺錯良民<br />\n個阿婆係自己人黎"},{"pid":"1e51bc4ea15fd39b16f2c9ceae6610394950e48b","tid":1565274,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3f6cf30b124b694d1a35886907d520b3f907f7d","tid":1565274,"uid":68654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c3d4746fe53f515df73412bb82836d6eb7d1e73","tid":1565274,"uid":68598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1e51bc4ea15fd39b16f2c9ceae6610394950e48b","tid":1565274,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"咁都要確定係邊戶 而家係連目標都錯"},{"pid":"2be376393f25a7fe79f04466c5b4f3fae2945810","tid":1565274,"uid":68654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1e51bc4ea15fd39b16f2c9ceae6610394950e48b","tid":1565274,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"你痴撚左線？<br />\n做大佢係需要，但唔會係向弱者抽刃<br />\n而且仲要係自己人"},{"pid":"b2c79849d8119d2e6810cea1be8f19ab76881f66","tid":1565274,"uid":68654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f00527ee13b756aae9f